            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12300,
            "LocalizeKR": "…저기, 선생님…\n혹시 괜찮으시다면…",
            "LocalizeJP": "…あの、先生…\nもし、よろしければ…。",
